{"tid":1387555,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"酌情檢控","createTime":"2019-07-30T14:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T14:33:18.000Z","uid":166070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96189a20edbcd4503aa95c17bd594939ebecf339","tid":1387555,"uid":166070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:29:15.000Z","msg":"有冇法律既巴打可以解答<br />\n如果律政司要基於公眾利益撤控<br />\n應該係聽日提堂個時做定咩時間做<br />\n人民有冇可能用公眾利益角度逼使律政司撤控?<br />\n<br />\n酌情檢控 <br />\n<br />\n《刑事訴訟程序條例》第15(1)條指出：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo; 律政司司長在任何案件中如認為，為了社會公正而不需要其參與，則並非一定需要檢控任何被控人。 &rdquo;<br />\n所以，公眾利益便成為是否提出檢控的最終考慮問題。律政司可以在考慮名方面的情況後，行使酌情權並不提出檢控。1999年，受廣大爭議的胡仙案便是其中之一的例子。"},{"pid":"79c64ed878e8e95b482de19c9e2834379991d8e8","tid":1387555,"uid":108636,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:29:29.000Z","msg":"黑警加人工係好合理既事？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1387030\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1387030</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f314c378d0b3425358585cce987dd5cc78062a89","tid":1387555,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:30:26.000Z","msg":"隨時"},{"pid":"1cdbb770c721b32d10b294623d9f20c1c9de13bf","tid":1387555,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:30:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">律政司司長</span></span>"},{"pid":"27bd288738a8e96ea27bf2755eaf186bab070ffa","tid":1387555,"uid":288511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:32:15.000Z","msg":"利申: Law撚<br />\n<br />\n你覺得聽命於中央嘅仆街鄭驊會行使酌情權？"},{"pid":"bfcc13104e3e8100311f921bdb878cb02eb62ce8","tid":1387555,"uid":25183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27bd288738a8e96ea27bf2755eaf186bab070ffa","tid":1387555,"uid":288511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:32:15.000Z","msg":"利申: Law撚<br />\n<br />\n你覺得聽命於中央嘅仆街鄭驊會行使酌情權？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:33:18.000Z","msg":"對白衫暴徒行使酌情權就有可能發生"}]}